TITLE: LULC to wetlands map - Python module for post-processing LULC classifications
AUTHORS: Migone, L., Schivo, F., Verón, S., Banchero, S., and Grimson, R.
EMAIL: lmigone@unsam.edu.ar
LICENSE: GNU AGPL v3.0
